Notebook[{
Cell[TextData[StyleBox["Escola de Engenharia da UFRJ\nDepartamento de Eletrot\
\[EAcute]cnica\nEE-456 Linhas de Transmiss\[ATilde]o\nProf. Sandoval Carneiro \
Jr. \nPrimeiro Per\[IAcute]odo de 2003", "Title"]], "Section",
  CellDingbat->None],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Primeira Quest\[ATilde]o", "Section"],

Cell[TextData[{
  "Uma linha de transmiss\[ATilde]o tem 300 milhas de comprimento e supre uma \
carga de 400MVA com fator de pot\[EHat]ncia unit\[AAcute]rio a 345kV. Um \
banco de capacitores deve ser instalado na ",
  StyleBox["metade do comprimento desta LT, a fim de compensar 60% da imped\
\[AHat]ncia da linha. As constantes ABCD para 150 milhas da linha \
s\[ATilde]o:\n     A = D = 0,9534 0,3",
    Evaluatable->False,
    AspectRatioFixed->True,
    FontFamily->"Times New Roman"],
  StyleBox["o",
    Evaluatable->False,
    AspectRatioFixed->True,
    FontFamily->"Times New Roman",
    FontVariations->{"CompatibilityType"->"Superscript"}],
  StyleBox["       B = 90,33 84,1",
    Evaluatable->False,
    AspectRatioFixed->True,
    FontFamily->"Times New Roman"],
  StyleBox["o",
    Evaluatable->False,
    AspectRatioFixed->True,
    FontFamily->"Times New Roman",
    FontVariations->{"CompatibilityType"->"Superscript"}],
  StyleBox["         C = 0,00101490,4",
    Evaluatable->False,
    AspectRatioFixed->True,
    FontFamily->"Times New Roman"],
  StyleBox["o",
    Evaluatable->False,
    AspectRatioFixed->True,
    FontFamily->"Times New Roman",
    FontVariations->{"CompatibilityType"->"Superscript"}],
  StyleBox[" mhos",
    Evaluatable->False,
    AspectRatioFixed->True,
    FontFamily->"Times New Roman"],
  StyleBox["\n",
    Evaluatable->False,
    AspectRatioFixed->True,
    FontFamily->"Arial",
    FontSize->12],
  StyleBox["Pede-se: ",
    Evaluatable->False,
    AspectRatioFixed->True,
    FontFamily->"Times New Roman"]
}], "Text",
  Evaluatable->False,
  AspectRatioFixed->True],

Cell["a. Determine as constantes ABCD para o banco de capacitores", "Text",
  Evaluatable->False,
  AspectRatioFixed->True],

Cell[BoxData[{
    \(\(A150 = 0.9534\ Exp[I\ 0.3*Pi/180];\)\), "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
    \(\(D150 = A150;\)\), "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
    \(\(B150 = 90.33\ Exp[I\ 84.1*Pi/180];\)\), "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
    \(\(C150 = 0.001014\ Exp[I\ 90.4*Pi/180];\)\)}], "Input"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    RowBox[{"Q150", "=", 
      RowBox[{"(", GridBox[{
            {"A150", "B150"},
            {"C150", "D150"}
            }], ")"}]}]], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    FormBox[
      RowBox[{"(", "\[NoBreak]", GridBox[{
            {\(\(\(0.9533869310286966`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                0.004991967916875427`\ \[ImaginaryI]\), \
\(\(\(9.285249847992013`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                89.85150547019434`\ \[ImaginaryI]\)},
            {\(\(-7.078997942132961`*^-6\) + 
                0.0010139752895352702`\ \[ImaginaryI]\), \
\(\(\(0.9533869310286966`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                0.004991967916875427`\ \[ImaginaryI]\)}
            },
          ColumnAlignments->{Decimal}], "\[NoBreak]", ")"}], 
      TraditionalForm]], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["para 300mi de LT basta quadrar a matriz Q150", "Text",
  Evaluatable->False,
  AspectRatioFixed->True],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    \(Q300 = Q150 . Q150\)], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    FormBox[
      RowBox[{"(", "\[NoBreak]", GridBox[{
            {\(\(\(0.8177487839737473`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                0.01829750922483113`\ \[ImaginaryI]\), \
\(\(\(16.80780004764322`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                171.41920543575617`\ \[ImaginaryI]\)},
            {\(\(-0.000023621512473346287`\) + 
                0.001933350902596709`\ \[ImaginaryI]\), \
\(\(\(0.8177487839737473`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                0.01829750922483113`\ \[ImaginaryI]\)}
            },
          ColumnAlignments->{Decimal}], "\[NoBreak]", ")"}], 
      TraditionalForm]], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
como o banco de capacitores deve compensar cerca de 60% da LT de 300mi temos:\
\
\>", "Text",
  Evaluatable->False,
  AspectRatioFixed->True],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    \(Xc = \(-I\)\ 0.6\ Im[Q300[\([1, 2]\)]]\)], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    \(TraditionalForm\`\(-102.85152326145369`\)\ \[ImaginaryI]\)], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["o quadripolo para o banco de capacitores \[EAcute]:", "Text",
  Evaluatable->False,
  AspectRatioFixed->True],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    RowBox[{\(Acap = 1\), ";", \(Bcap = Xc\), ";", \(Ccap = 0.0\), 
      ";", \(Dcap = 1\), ";", 
      RowBox[{"Qcap", "=", 
        RowBox[{"(", GridBox[{
              {"Acap", "Bcap"},
              {"Ccap", "Dcap"}
              }], ")"}]}]}]], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    FormBox[
      RowBox[{"(", "\[NoBreak]", GridBox[{
            {"1", \(\(-102.85152326145369`\)\ \[ImaginaryI]\)},
            {"0.`", "1"}
            },
          ColumnAlignments->{Decimal}], "\[NoBreak]", ")"}], 
      TraditionalForm]], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
b. Determine as constantes ABCD para LT 300milhas, compensada pelo banco de \
capacitores;\
\>", "Text",
  Evaluatable->False,
  AspectRatioFixed->True],

Cell["\<\
o quadripolo para o conjunto LT150mi+Capacitor serie+LT150mi \[EAcute]:\
\>", "Text",
  Evaluatable->False,
  AspectRatioFixed->True],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    \(Qtotal = Q150 . Qcap . Q150\)], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    FormBox[
      RowBox[{"(", "\[NoBreak]", GridBox[{
            {\(\(\(0.9171728266392363`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                0.019512263494642676`\ \[ImaginaryI]\), \
\(\(\(17.786797820043017`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                77.93522195561052`\ \[ImaginaryI]\)},
            {\(\(-0.00002509803433390171`\) + 
                0.0020390921191733944`\ \[ImaginaryI]\), \
\(\(\(0.9171728266392364`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                0.019512263494642676`\ \[ImaginaryI]\)}
            },
          ColumnAlignments->{Decimal}], "\[NoBreak]", ")"}], 
      TraditionalForm]], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
c. Determine a tens\[ATilde]o fase neutro e a corrente no lado emissor para a \
LT a plena carga, bem como a queda percentual da tens\[ATilde]o na LT sem \
compensa\[CCedilla]\[ATilde]o\
\>", "Text",
  Evaluatable->False,
  AspectRatioFixed->True],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    RowBox[{\(Vr = 345\ 10^3\), ";", \(Ir = 400\ 10^6/\((Sqrt[3]\ Vr)\)\), 
      ";", 
      RowBox[{"R", "=", 
        RowBox[{"(", GridBox[{
              {"Vr"},
              {"Ir"}
              }], ")"}]}]}]], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    FormBox[
      RowBox[{"(", "\[NoBreak]", GridBox[{
            {"345000"},
            {\(80000\/\(69\ \@3\)\)}
            }], "\[NoBreak]", ")"}], TraditionalForm]], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    \(Snc = Q300 . R\)], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    FormBox[
      RowBox[{"(", "\[NoBreak]", GridBox[{
            {\(\(\(293374.33091383235`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                121059.21970008047`\ \[ImaginaryI]\)},
            {\(\(\(539.2447585523271`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                679.254260672915`\ \[ImaginaryI]\)}
            },
          ColumnAlignments->{Decimal}], "\[NoBreak]", ")"}], 
      TraditionalForm]], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
em coordenadas polares com tens\[ATilde]o fase-fase\
\>", "Text",
  Evaluatable->False,
  AspectRatioFixed->True],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    RowBox[{"(", GridBox[{
          {\(Abs[Snc[\([1, 1]\)]] \[Angle]\ [
                180/Pi\ Arg[Snc[\([1, 1]\)]]]\)},
          {\(Abs[Snc[\([2, 1]\)]] \[Angle]\ [180/Pi\ Arg[Snc[\([2, 1]\)]]]\)}
          }], ")"}]], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    FormBox[
      RowBox[{"(", "\[NoBreak]", GridBox[{
            {\(317370.1824581685`\ \(\[Angle](22.423208363935224`)\)\)},
            {\(867.2780755146908`\ \(\[Angle](51.55472554563087`)\)\)}
            }], "\[NoBreak]", ")"}], TraditionalForm]], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    \(\[CapitalDelta]vp = Vr\  - Abs[Snc[\([1, 1]\)]]\)], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    \(TraditionalForm\`27629.817541831522`\)], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    \(Vsn = Abs[Snc[\([1, 1]\)]]/Sqrt[3]\)], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    \(TraditionalForm\`183233.76027498423`\)], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
d. Determine a tens\[ATilde]o no lado receptor fase neutro e a corrente no \
lado emissor para a LT a plena carga, bem como a queda percentual da tens\
\[ATilde]o na LT sem compensa\[CCedilla]\[ATilde]o. Considerando a tens\
\[ATilde]o no lado emissor como a tens\[ATilde]o nominal temos:\
\>", "Text",
  Evaluatable->False,
  AspectRatioFixed->True],

Cell[BoxData[
    RowBox[{\(Vsc = 345\ 10^3\), ";", \(Irc = 0.0\), ";", 
      RowBox[{"Qrc", "=", 
        RowBox[{"(", GridBox[{
              {"Vrc"},
              {"0"}
              }], ")"}]}], ";", " ", 
      RowBox[{"Qsc", "=", 
        RowBox[{"(", GridBox[{
              {"Vsc"},
              {"Is"}
              }], ")"}]}], ";"}]], "Input"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    \(Vrc = 1/Qtotal[\([1, 1]\)]\ Vsc\)], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    \(TraditionalForm\`\(\(375985.7621163317`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) - 
      7998.8558836072025`\ \[ImaginaryI]\)], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
    \(Isc = Qtotal[\([2, 1]\)]\ Vsc\)], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[
    \(TraditionalForm\`\(-8.65882184519609`\) + 
      703.486781114821`\ \[ImaginaryI]\)], "Output"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]]
},
